OL,6,F"So starting today, I can announce
OL,7,Fthis government will begin the biggest
OL,8,Fsustained increase in defence spending
OL,9,Fsince the end of the Cold War.
OL,11,F"We will deliver our commitment to
OL,12,Fspend 2.5%. of GDP on defence, but we
OL,13,Fwill bring it forward so that we reach
OL,14,Fthat level in 2027, and we will
OL,15,Fmaintain that for the rest of this
OL,16,FParliament.
OL,18,F"And let me spell it out, that means
OL,19,Fspending #13.4 billion more on defence
OL,20,Fevery year from 2027."
