OL,6,FThe decision comes following rising
OL,7,Ftensions between Europe, the US and
OL,8,FRussia over the future of Ukraine.
OL,10,FTrump has been demanding that Europe
OL,11,Fspends more on defence, while the
OL,12,Ftransatlantic approach to the war in
OL,13,FUkraine has come under strain after US
OL,14,Finterventions such as the US president
OL,15,Fsuggesting that Ukrainian President
OL,16,FVolodymyr Zelensky is a "dictator".
