OL,6,FIt comes after ITV News' Robert Peston
OL,7,Frevealed the government would commit
OL,8,Fto increasing defence spending to 2.5%
OL,9,Fof GDP by the end of the decade - or
OL,10,Fmuch sooner - with Treasury and
OL,11,FDowning Street officials working to
OL,12,Fget the numbers together ahead of
OL,13,FStarmer's meeting with Donald Trump
OL,14,Fthis week.
OL,16,FThe prime minister will visit Trump
OL,17,Ffor the first time since he became US
OL,18,Fpresident for a second term in a
OL,19,Fhistoric meeting in Washington DC on
OL,20,FThursday.
