OL,6,FStarmer will be hoping to show the US
OL,7,Fpresident the UK's commitment to
OL,8,Fbolster its armed forces and spending
OL,9,Fafter Trump said Nato members should
OL,10,Fbe spending 5% GDP on defence.
OL,12,FChancellor Rachel Reeves signalled
OL,13,Flast week that spending cuts elsewhere
OL,14,Fcould be on the way in a bid to boost
OL,15,Fthe nation's defence budget, warning
OL,16,Fshe will have to make "difficult
OL,17,Fchoices".
