OL,6,F"Recognising the priority of defence
OL,7,Fspending in the world that we live in
OL,8,Ftoday means that we will have to make
OL,9,Fdifficult choices so that we can spend
OL,10,Fthat money that is needed to keep our
OL,11,Fcountry safe," she told ITV News.
OL,13,FBut, ahead of the government's
OL,14,Fannouncement, Leader of the Opposition
OL,15,FKemi Badenoch said committing to
OL,16,Fspending 2.5% by 2030 is "no longer
OL,17,Fsufficient".
